'''Mount Thunderstone''' was an active volcano on the [[Endor/Legends|Forest Moon of Endor]]. A dark and forbidding place, Thunderstone was home to [[Morag]], the [[Tulgah/Legends|Tulgah]] witch, who lived in a [[Morag's lair|castle]] on the mountain until her death in [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]]. The area was under constant surveillance by [[Yuzzum/Legends|Yuzzum]] guards, many of them mounted on [[Rakazzak beast/Legends|rakazzak beasts]].

